        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for the letter, photograph, and kind words about CD’s scientific work. [See <hi rend="doubleUnderline">8088</hi>.]</p> 
            <p>CTEvS’s view of pseudova is new to CD;</p>
            <p>he has not yet received the recent work on parthenogenesis</p> 
<p>though he did receive the memoir on <hi rend="italic">Polistes</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
